ui le community locali si incontrano per condividere conoscenze, conoscersi e fare rete.</p></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Se non sai cos’è un meetup <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/guida-ai-meetup-di-wordpress/\">leggi qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tutti i meetup WordPress italiani attivi sono <a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni, <em>in ordine cronologico</em>, si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 8 mag, ore 19:00, &#8220;Workshop Git per WordPress developers&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/300469306\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 10 mag, ore 18:00, &#8220;Patterns for the win (talk in inglese)&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/romawordpress/events/300616729\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pisa</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 15 mag, ore 18:00, &#8220;NO MORE THUMBNAILS!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/300782270\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 16 mag, ore 18:30, &#8220;Nomade digitale grazie a WordPress&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/300310244\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color has-extra-large-font-size\">… articolo in aggiornamento…</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\"